snippet.title: Life Makeover - Official Global Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Download Life Makeover Globally now:  https://yslzm-seareal.onelink.me/wcP9...
Download Life Makeover in Vietnam now:  https://yslzm-vn.onelink.me/w1YS/w4e6...
Come to this brand-new virtual world where you can create your very own avatar, customize dress-up and makeup, design one-and-only garments by yourself, build your dream house, and chill with your besties!

Born in Romance, Makeover in Life!

To show big thanks for your long-term support and love, besides in-game rewards, we have prepared so many events on social media, and you will have chance to win iPhone 14 pro, Dyson hair dryer, necklace and CHANEL lipsticks. Also you may share a $20,000 prize pool on Content Creator Program. Join our communities for more event info now!

 Facebook:  https://www.facebook.com/LifeMakeover
 VK:  https://vk.com/lifemakeover
 Discord:  https://discord.gg/Rj4dYTgw3s
